Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.21,0:23:48.81,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,手を切るくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:53.58,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,痛ッ!證明したい マイ存在自体
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.38,0:23:56.93,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,永久ライン
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.18,0:24:01.67,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,囲い込まれても セーフティライン
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.16,0:24:05.15,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,「Wanna take you high ? 」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.42,0:24:10.11,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,揺れる銀河 君はスマイル
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.52,0:24:13.44,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,触れていたい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.66,0:24:18.09,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,罰則なったとか 聞きたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.85,0:24:23.50,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,論にほだされ論理捨て
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.51,0:24:28.75,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,理性なきリスクゲームなど 申請
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.86,0:24:36.66,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,稀代の痛いのを以って 光彩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.05,0:24:44.96,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,実際とアン実際とをミステイツク
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.28,0:24:53.00,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,一切の理解の向こうに So Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.50,0:24:57.16,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,So Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.52,0:25:01.12,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,So Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.71,0:25:09.52,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,So Fight!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-----TV-----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.14,0:00:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从前 世上的诸多星辰混杂在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时人与神之间的界限还很模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.32,0:00:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这 是个围绕一家之间的爱与重生的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.94,0:01:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:02:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重逢之日 一定会到来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天上好像飘着很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年的开站…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.45,0:02:52.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又开始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「开站」?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:02:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么要打开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:02:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么东西要飘过去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们最好暂时不要接近八濑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为对八濑来说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开站是她最讨厌的事情之一了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扔掉 扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飘走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说我要回去了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:03:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怕呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.68,0:04:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她啊 每次到了开站的时候就要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别乱跑 别乱闹 别弄坏东西!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是稍微玩玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拿你那锤子弄坏的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来能修好也修不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.45,0:04:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的东西不是能修好的么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥 为啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我还想问呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:04:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人没了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂! 你们也过来帮忙收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个坏不掉 这个也坏不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要的东西也不会损坏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世界真让人难以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 通过开站把不需要的东西飘走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.92,0:05:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也算是合情合理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最心爱的茶杯呢!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里去了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:34.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八——濑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.94,0:07:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八——濑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 大家都在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八濑也在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:53.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要嘛 让我们进去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八濑?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是开站啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天上飘的东西 都会聚集在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之就是要从这里找出八濑的茶杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.32,0:09:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我凭啥非得做这些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八濑的家里好像也囤了好多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但为什么不丢掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:10:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 要那样珍藏起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.61,0:10:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开站是为了扔掉这里的垃圾 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那八濑为什么不扔东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八濑喜欢的是哪个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:10:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都没有我的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做的真好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长得好高啊 八濑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎能丢掉这些…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一件都充满了和妈妈的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能丢掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个娃娃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话 拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把珍贵的东西飘走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会飘到妈妈那里的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样一来 妈妈就一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娃娃…回来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有回来吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:17.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是飘走的娃娃 还是妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.99,0:13:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就没办法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟那杯子代表她和妈妈的珍贵回忆嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿 吽 我们再加把劲!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好——
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才感觉是能找到的呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「感觉」…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没感觉 没感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到 找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.07,0:13:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了代替找不着的八濑的杯子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就想让我把自己的杯子交出来?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:13:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求您了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还 还请您多通融一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这杯子对我来说同样珍贵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会轻易拱手让人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了八濑那更是绝无可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然敢在这里挥舞你那武器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是八濑在开站时候的焦躁不安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是她讨厌人类龟缩山中的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追根究底 都是住持你的错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.09,0:14:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使你是八濑的哥哥 把她最珍贵的东西飘走…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:14:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…也是不对的吧?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 那杯子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.45,0:15:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对要拿下!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何你也要这么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.73,0:15:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就拿拿看吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对要拿到!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 这帮人吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对要拿到!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么呀 好喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要尝尝不?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八濑喝这个 可能还早了点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.59,0:16:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八濑又要变成鬼啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耐不住性子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生气啦生气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没生气呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.04,0:16:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画中诞生的鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…这就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用去做什么改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直保持这样就行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我是画出来的 不如画得跟妈妈一样多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八濑也很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:17:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我长大了 一定要变得跟妈妈一样!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.01,0:17:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈都在包容着我的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.77,0:17:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来都关怀着我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点点地 妈妈让我这鬼的心平静了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…妈妈已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.51,0:17:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不能回到过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经失去的珍贵回忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.67,0:17:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也不会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.67,0:18:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八濑—— 八濑!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.47,0:18:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家这是怎么搞的 这么邋遢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 给你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.51,0:18:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.83,0:18:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的杯子虽然大家都去找了 但是找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经失去的珍贵回忆 再也不会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:18:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是呢 我们也不能空手而回
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就去鞍马寺把它「借」来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鞍马…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.45,0:19:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不 不是的不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个住持给我们的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然他一开始不情愿 满腹的牢骚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 他还是给我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是为了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鞍马…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的感受 我的悲伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.35,0:19:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鞍马怎么可能明白!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然失败了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八濑…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你闹过火啦——!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「把珍贵的东西飘走 一定会飘到妈妈那里的」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「那样一来 妈妈就一定会回来的」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.31,0:21:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八濑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.49,0:21:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好吧 八濑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八濑…这冷不丁地干什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.95,0:21:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了迁就我的任性 真是太谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过到头来 还是找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.82,0:21:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就用那个杯子代替吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.33,0:21:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.16,0:21:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我会很珍惜地用它的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.51,0:22:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八濑 还不到回去的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.97,0:22:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且向你道个谢 鞍马
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.12,0:22:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.63,0:22:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么一回事 先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫「就这么一回事」…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.72,0:22:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 八濑 到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.31,0:22:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八濑!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.51,0:22:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦不烦!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.94,0:22:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全搞不懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.48,0:22:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.57,0:22:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开站也没剩多少时间了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.39,0:23:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们闹够没!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼好疼好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.64,0:23:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 明惠你把那念珠也扔掉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.47,0:23:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.41,0:23:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.95,0:23:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世上有些东西 是无论如何也不舍得扔的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个——!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.31,0:25:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从琴他们到来 我心中就一直焦躁不安
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.73,0:25:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又蠢又任性还狂妄 只有我一个人遭殃
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.76,0:25:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她根本不关心他人的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.08,0:25:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管发生什么 都不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.60,0:25:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 年轻的三儿子的烦恼与开始与结束
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.34,0:25:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他们回来之前 一切都不会变
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
